# SmartCafé — Backend

Tech Stack
-React, Vite , TypeScript
-Tailwind CSS
-Zustand (global state)
-React Hook Form (validate in form)
-React Router (routing)
-Axios (API connect to backend)
-React-toastify (Toast Notification)
-zod (validate)


Development
-git clone https://github.com/Tanatusss/smartcafe_frontend.git
-cd smartcafe_frontend
-pnpm i
-pnpm dev

Browser default : http://localhost:5173


Role
-USER
-BARRISTA (ถึงจะสามารถเข้าถึงหน้าDASH BOARD)



pnpm create vite smartcafe-frontend --template react-ts
pnpm install
pnpm install tailwindcss @tailwindcss/vite
pnpm add react-router-dom
pnpm add -D @types/node
pnpm add zustand
pnpm add axios
pnpm add react-toastify
pnpm add jwt-decode
pnpm add zod react-hook-form @hookform/resolvers

